Super Heroes Behind Audify:
Libraries used,
   1. Realm - http://realm.io
   2. Butterknife - http://jakewharton.github.io/butterknife/
   3. Otto - http://square.github.io/otto/
   4. Timber - https://github.com/JakeWharton/timber
   5. AppIntro - https://github.com/PaoloRotolo/AppIntro
   6. RecyclerView FastScroller - https://github.com/danoz73/RecyclerViewFastScroller
   7. Android-Location-Tracker - https://github.com/quentin7b/android-location-tracker
   8. Material-Dialogs - https://github.com/afollestad/material-dialogs
   9. AutoLabelUI - https://github.com/DavidPizarro/AutoLabelUI
  10. Android-InApp-Billing-V3 - https://github.com/anjlab/android-inapp-billing-v3

